{"word":"G3580 - ξενοδοχέω - xenodochéō - xen-od-okh-eh'-o - Lodge strangers","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ξενοδοχέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">xenodochéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">xen-od-okh-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Lodge strangers</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"விருந்தினரை - உபசரி"},{"paragraph":"to receive and entertain hospitably, to be hospitable"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G3581 - ξένος - xénos - xen'-os/3581\">G3581</a> and <a href=\"#/G1209 - δέχομαι - déchomai - dekh'-om-ahee/1209\">G1209</a>; to <i>be hospitable:</i> - lodge strangers.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3578/3578\">G3578</a>, <a href=\"#/G3579/3579\">G3579</a>, <a href=\"#/G3580/3580\">G3580</a>, <a href=\"#/G3581/3581\">G3581</a>, <a href=\"#/G5381/5381\">G5381</a>, <a href=\"#/G5382/5382\">G5382</a>"}]}